Package: bunsen-welcome
Section: misc
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 bunsen-common (>= 11.1-1),
 laptop-detect,
 lsb-release,
 xterm | x-terminal-emulator
Description: BunsenLabs welcome script
 Post installation script for BunsenLabs Linux,
 to install some optional extra packages.

